title: Bruce Springsteen 100 Greatest Songs - Rolling Stone Magazine
description:
Bruce Springsteen's 100 Greatest Songs compiled by Rolling Stone magazine.  

I added 20 more which round out the set, since some of RS's choices (i.e. Jack of All Trades) are a bit perplexing.

Songs 1-100 are part of RS's list, and songs    101-120 are mine in random order.

I am not saying this torrent is perfect, there is some inconsistent metadata and others, but I was tired of workng on this and just wanted to get it out to you.
